        <h3 class="head">FAQ</h3>
        <hr style="height: 2px; background-color: black; border: none;">
        <br>
        <h3 id="q1">BUY - ORDER - TRACK ORDER</h3>
        <br>
        <div id="a1">
            <p><strong>1. HOW TO BUY AT SNEAKFREAK?</strong></p>
            <p>You can order our products directly on the website following these simple steps:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Select the product you like.</li>
                <li>Choose the appropriate product size and quantity.</li>
                <li>Complete other ordering steps on the system.</li>
                <li>Receive successful order confirmation email from SneakFreak system.</li>
                <li>Please wait a few more days for the product to be delivered to you.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>2. WHEN I ORDER ON THE SNEAKFREAK WEBSITE, WILL I RECEIVE AN EMAIL OR CALL TO CONFIRM THAT I HAVE
                    SUCCESSFULLY PLACED MY ORDER?</strong></p>
            <p>Currently, after successfully placing an order at the website, you will receive an order
                confirmation via the email you used to register along with an order confirmation call from SneakFreak '
                Customer Service department. <br>Some important notes: </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Customer Service will contact you via phone call when there is a problem with your order, during the
                    time frame: Monday - Saturday, 8:00 am to 5:00 pm.</li>
                <li>SneakFreak always tries to contact you 02 calls/day and in 02 consecutive days. If after the above
                    deadline we still cannot contact to discuss the arising problem, your order will be canceled on the
                    system.</li>
                <li> At some times the system is not stable (no confirmation email sent), you can proactively contact
                    Customer Service to receive order information.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>3. HOW CAN I TRACK, CANCEL OR CHANGE MY ORDER?</strong></p>
            <p>To look up your order, you can access the Order Tracking section , fill in all the information about the
                "order code" and "email/phone number" that you registered.<br>In the order lookup section, in addition
                to tracking the processing process, you can also directly
                cancel the order if the order has not been transferred to the delivery unit. In case the order has been
                transferred to the delivery unit by SneakFreak, please contact the Customer Service department directly
                via
                hotline 1900 3004 for more detailed instructions.<br>In addition, you can also contact Customer Service
                in case of changes to order information or if you
                want to change to another product.</p>
            <p><strong>4. FOR ORDERS PAID BY ONLINE PAYMENT METHOD, WILL I GET A REFUND IF I CANCEL THE ORDER?</strong>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Where such cancellation request meets SneakFreak's instructions for changing or cancelling
                    transactions
                    , we will refund your payment for any reason.</li>
                <li>The refund time depends on the type of card you used to pay, usually 1-3 business days for domestic
                    cards, and 7-10 business days for international cards from the time the order was canceled. In some
                    cases, there are problems with the transaction processing from the bank or payment gateway, the
                    refund time may be longer.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>5. CAN I CHECK THE PRODUCT BEFORE RECEIVING IT?</strong></p>
            <p>Currently, the order sent to you will be carefully sealed by us and you will not be able to check the
                product
                before receiving the goods to avoid various problems arising during transportation and transaction that
                SneakFreak cannot control. We hope you understand.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
