        <h3 id="q3">PROMOTION PROGRAM</h3>
        <br>
        <div id="a3">
            <p>Currently, we are running the following unlimited promotions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>FREE SHIPPING program nationwide with each bill from 50$(1.298.124 VND), applied to all products on
                    website.</li>
                <li>The BUY MORE - PAY LESS program applies to products classified as Second Hand on both online and
                    offline channels , specifically:</li>
                <li style="list-style: none;">
                    <ul>
                        <li>5% discount on secondhand sneaker when buying 2 sneakers of the Second hand in one bill.
                        </li>
                        <li>10% discount on secondhand sneaker when buying 3 sneakers of the Second hand in one bill.
                        </li>
                        <li>15% discount on secondhand sneaker when buying 4 sneakers of the Second hand in one bill.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>The BUY 2 GET 10% OFF program applies to all Sneakers on web channels.
                    Specifically, when you buy 2 or more sneakers in one bill, the system will automatically
                    calculate a 10% discount for you on total bill.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Notes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The system will automatically apply the discount when the invoice meets the conditions on the
                    “Purchase Information” page.</li>
                <li>Free Shipping program only applies to shipping fees, not applicable in cases of exchange or
                    warranty.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr style="border: 1px dashed gray;">
        <br>
        <h3 id="q4">DELIVERY - TRANSPORTATION</h3>
        <br>
        <div id="a4">
            <p><strong>1. DO I PAY SHIPPING CHARGE WHEN I PLACE AN ORDER AND HOW MUCH IS IT?</strong></p>
            <p>Shipping fee will always be calculated at 5% of total bill and will be displayed after you fill in all
                necessary
                information on the “Purchase Information” page.</p>
            <p><strong>2. HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE TO RECEIVE MY PRODUCT FROM SNEAKFREAK?</strong></p>
            <p>Estimated delivery time in Ho Chi Minh City will take 2-3 days; suburbs and major cities will take 3-5
                days; other provinces and cities will take about 5-7 days.</p>
            <p>Notes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The above delivery time is calculated from the date the shipping unit starts delivering the goods,
                    not including order processing time.</li>
                <li>Orders will not be delivered on Sundays and Holidays.</li>
                <li>At some times, the shipping will be overloaded, resulting in your order being delayed longer than
                    expected. We hope you understand and wait a few more days.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>3. DOES SNEAKFREAK SHIP INTERNATIONALLY?</strong></p>
            <p>Currently, we only support orders within Vietnam. For orders requiring shipping abroad, please contact
                Customer Service for detailed instructions.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr style="border: 1px dashed gray;">
        <br>
        <h3 id="q5">PRODUCT EXCHANGE - WARRANTY</h3>
        <br>
        <div id="a5">
            <p><strong>1. WHAT ARE SNEAKFREAK'S EXCHANGE POLICIES?</strong></p>
            <p>SneakFreak always hopes that each product that comes to you is truly suitable and makes you satisfied.
                However, we still have some regulations on exchanging goods for your reference in case you are not
                satisfied with the product after purchasing. Specifically as follows:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The exchange period for shoes and fashion products is 14 days from the date you receive the goods.
                </li>
                <li>No returns or refunds are accepted under any circumstances. We appreciate your understanding.</li>
                <li>Only one-time exchange is applicable.</li>
                <li>The exchanged product must be new, with intact stamps, boxes, labels and no signs of use, washing,
                    dirt or deformation.</li>
                <li> In case you want to exchange for another product, we still support you:
                    <ul>
                        <li>If the product you want to exchange is of equal or higher value, you will need to pay the
                            difference at the time of exchange (if any). </li>
                        <li>If you wish to exchange for a product of lower value, we will not refund.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>To exchange goods, please fill in all information and follow the instructions printed on the
                    Shipping Box included upon delivery.</li>
                <li>When exchanging goods, please pay one end of the shipping fee to SneakFreak online warehouse. We
                    will pay the return shipping fee to you after completing the product exchange.</li>
                <li> In case the product - size you want to exchange is out of stock at the online exchange warehouse
                    system, please choose another product.</li>
                <li>SneakFreak supports warranty within 06 months from the date of purchase in cases of loose glue,
                    broken thread,
                    broken sole or manufacturer's defect.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>3. HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE TO RECEIVE THE EXCHANGED AND WARRANTY PRODUCT WHEN I SEND IT BACK TO
                    SNEAKFREAK?</strong></p>
            <p>Upon receiving your returned product, depending on the form of "Exchange" or "Warranty", the Customer
                Service department will notify you of the estimated time you can receive your product back. Please
                believe that we always try to work to get the product back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>
